{"tid":1565691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】我建議將「藍絲」正名為「赤納粹分子」","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:22:28.000Z","uid":293677,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa35fecb7e5664bdf07a46ccd12f6559131b7d59","tid":1565691,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"自2010年代開始，中華人民共和國在新疆維吾爾自治區實施再教育營，進營人數達12萬[2][3][4]，中共亦被揭發在新疆摧毀清真寺[5]，更強逼維吾爾人社群在手機安裝間諜軟體[6]，安排當地家庭結對認親[7] ，而新疆人出門及回家必須掃臉進行人面辨識[8]，被批評有如納粹德國時代的集中營[1]。<br />\n<br />\n2014年起，中共亦在中國各省大肆強拆十字架， 至2015年，浙江省被強拆十字架的數字已達1200座[9]，但強拆行為在各省各地仍未有止息的跡象。2018年，河南省再起強拆十字架風波，超過4000間教會的十字架被拆，並掛上中華人民共和國國旗[10]。此舉被批儼如重演納粹德國逼害宗教人士的悲劇[11]。<br />\n<br />\n2018年，中國流亡作家余杰出版了《納粹中國》一書，敘述當今中國正出現邁向納粹德國的勢態[12]。 <br />\n<br />\n----維基百科<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B5%A4%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B2%25B9&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=f6a7e4d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B5%A4%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n藍絲所支持既係犯反人類罪行既中共 即係赤納粹<br />\n一個有良知香港人唔好再緃容呢D 赤納粹分子<br />\n點解佢地咁夠膽一個人同幾十個人 甚到幾百個人挑機??<br />\n因為佢地就係知道你地膽小懦弱<br />\n同埋有左膠一定會出黎阻止開佢拖<br />\n「停手，唔好打」<br />\n屌你咩!!<br />\n仲影相?仲拍片?仲圍住黎鬧?<br />\n直接開拖<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">私了</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕不能縱容 赤納粹分子<br />\n打一個就少一個<br />\n唔好俾佢地再害人 再害手足"},{"pid":"6a147766e433909ed979f955434fd1d4bdc4df62","tid":1565691,"uid":109780,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"赤納粹真係好中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n納粹中國好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7db7e7aef95334c1f74a1c4101be6ddb4593bd9","tid":1565691,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fT7W0O5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfT7W0O5.png&h=00ce2165&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n#赤納粹<br />\n#Chinazi"},{"pid":"d46e0824756eced677a25e984477f94227633f31","tid":1565691,"uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a147766e433909ed979f955434fd1d4bdc4df62","tid":1565691,"uid":109780,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"赤納粹真係好中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n納粹中國好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"赤納粹<br />\n維基百科，自由的百科全書<br />\n<br />\n赤納粹（英語：Chinazi），又稱納粹中國，是對中華人民共和國與納粹主義相似的行徑作批評而衍生的詞語[1]。"},{"pid":"4541c91e712785cd1727e63f4a4cb4d086d00c61","tid":1565691,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64a634a9427b2516dc0aaefba7390fbe8535de64","tid":1565691,"uid":164374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"支納分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8100c65ec8a152a98c5bcb429b3b90c85bad64","tid":1565691,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"講得好，要文宣<br />\n<br />\n全面打倒赤納粹份子"},{"pid":"fd852c837c3792ba820d4095b72a88c66f621999","tid":1565691,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54161bb7b5963b7f245ebfed028c1c5f9232fa3d","tid":1565691,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a147766e433909ed979f955434fd1d4bdc4df62","tid":1565